name: Mooninite Invaders v1.0
description:
This game only came to fruition because so many people in the discord server I was in where I sent the idea for this game kept saying they would play this if it was real. Now they can. If there is anything wrong with your copy of the game, please let me know in the comments and I will try to find what's wrong. Dedicated to the Ky's Hellhole Discord Server. :)

NOTE: I am not affiliated with Warner Bros. Discovery, this is just an Aqua Teen Hunger Force fan game.

Now on macOS and Linux!
